      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/european-stocks-see-most-inflows-in-decade-amid-defense-splurge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者将资金倾倒在欧洲股票中，近十年来未见，因为他们预计基础设施和国防上的支出将会增加。]]></description>
